Test Case 05: Wallet add funds 

Test Case Title: Wallet add funds 

Test Case ID: Wallet Add fundsFt - 03

Description: Verify that users can add funds

Preconditions:
The user is logged in and on the application's home screen.

Test Steps to add funds:
Click on wallet 
Click on Add funds 
select convinient method (Use card, Make transfer, Pay with USSD.
Use Card 
Enter Amount
add new card
Enter card number,  card expiry  and CVV
Click Pay
Continue to wallet to confirm new balance 

Bank transfer 
Copy account number and deposit the money

Pay with USSD
Enter Amount
Click top u
Copy the USSD code provide and make the payment 

Expected Results:
User should be able to add funds to the wallet

Actual Result: 

